post_content.caption: Viral: Kohli Fan Thrashed Mercilessly For Breaching Security To Touch Kohli's Feet I Watch
post_content.description:

However, the fan was later reportedly thrashed by bouncers, a moment also caught on video, requested to be blurred. Kohli intervened, urging security for leniency, highlighting this as a memorable yet controversial fan moment, sparking widespread online discussion.

post_content.caption: LIVE: MEA Briefing on Indian National killed in Israel | Indian Nationals duped in Russia | Watch
post_content.description:
MEA statement on Indians in Russian Army: Several Indian nationals have been duped to work with the Russian Army. We have strongly taken up the matter with the Russian government for early discharge of such Indian nationals. Strong action has been initiated against agents and unscrupulous elements who recruited them on false pretexts and promises. The CBI yesterday busted a major human trafficking network conducting searches in several cities and collecting incriminating evidence. A case of human trafficking has been registered against several agents.  We once again appeal to Indian nationals to not be swayed by offers made by agents for support jobs with the Russian Army. This is fraught with danger and risk to life. We remain committed to the early release of our nationals serving as support staff with the Russian Army and their eventual return home.

post_content.caption: India Snaps At Biden Govt As U.S Doubles Down On Kejriwal Remarks; 'Unacceptable'
post_content.description:
India has strongly rebuked the Biden administration over comments regarding Arvind Kejriwal's arrest, labeling them as "unwarranted" and "unacceptable." The Ministry of External Affairs (MEA) emphasized India's pride in its independent and robust democratic institutions while also hitting back at U.S. remarks on the Congress party's claim of frozen bank accounts affecting their election campaign funds. The U.S., in turn, reiterated its call for fair, transparent, and timely legal processes in Kejriwal's case. This diplomatic exchange unfolded just hours after India summoned senior U.S. diplomat Gloria Berbena on March 26, with the meeting lasting for 40 minutes, indicating heightened tensions and exchanges between the two countries.

post_content.caption: IPL 2024 LIVE: Rajasthan Vs Delhi Match Preview | Rishabh Pant Looks For First Win | Cricket Calling
post_content.description:
#ipl2024 #cricketcalling #ipl #dcvsrr #rishabhpant 

The upcoming eighth match of IPL 2024 will showcase a thrilling clash between Rajasthan Royals (RR) and Delhi Capitals (DC) at Jaipur's Sawai Mansingh Stadium on Thursday, March 28. DC suffered a setback in their IPL 2024 debut, falling to Punjab Kings in their opening match. Conversely, Rajasthan Royals secured their first victory this season against Lucknow Super Giants in Jaipur on March 24. With their next home game on the horizon, RR is determined to continue their winning streak. The encounter promises high stakes as DC seeks redemption while RR aims to consolidate their position in the early stages of the tournament.
